{"type":"message","id":"1129c4d0","parentId":"289a6c8f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:19:30.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The session-summary file is empty (no actual conversation content from the previous session). This is expected since the previous session was also empty/startup.\n\nThe real question is: did the bootstrap hook successfully inject this empty session-summary into the current session? Based on my startup sequence, I did read the session-summary file and found it empty, then read the daily memory. So the bootstrap IS working - it found the file, read it, and I acted on it.\n\nBut the user is asking if the \"完整链路\" (complete chain) has been verified. Let me think about what that means:\n\n1. ephemeral → session-summary (writing step) - ✅ documented in cron and hooks\n\n\n2. session-summary → bootstrap injection (reading step) - ✅ I just verified this by reading it\n3. bootstrap → LLM context - ✅ I received it in my context\n4. Three-layer memory chain (ephemeral/session-summary/MEMORY.md) - the logic is sound\n\nThe full chain is functioning end-to-end, though the previous session was empty so there wasn't much to preserve. The critical piece is that bootstrap successfully injected the session-summary into my context, confirming the mechanism works.","thinkingSignature":"504b702af3e60df17e8ab77f69b40242757896c138d7400f188e2b1b6ad64a5b"},{"type":"text","text":"<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户问\"完整链路跑通了吗\"——指的是 MEMORY.md 中记录的\"三层记忆链路\"和 bootstrap 注入机制是否端到端验证完成。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n链路分三段：\n1. ephemeral → session-summary 文件（本次 session 的决策数据写入）\n2. session-summary 文件 → bootstrap hook 读取\n3. bootstrap 文件 → 注入 LLM 上下文\n\n刚才 /new 触发 bootstrap，我成功读到了 session-summary 文件内容并基于它做了启动判断。链路 2+3 已验证。\nephemeral 那段需要看本次 session 的决策数据是否正常写入。\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\nephemeral 目录在 session 结束后会怎样处理？本次是 /new 后立即提问，还没产生多少决策数据。另外 session-summary hook 应该在 session 结束时生成 summary，但现在这个 summary 是空的——说明上一个 session 确实没有任何会话内容（只有系统消息）。\n\n### 4. 最终决策\n链路本身是通的。总结现状并告知用户。\n</thinking>\n\n链路 2+3 刚才已经验证了——/new 后 bootstrap hook 正确读取了 `*-session-summary.md` 文件（就是那个空的），我收到了它的内容。\n\nephemeral 那段要看你现在这句话执行后产生的决策数据。等这次 session 结束（下次 /new）时，hook 会把数据写入 session-summary 文件，届时就能验证完整闭环。\n\n现在 M2.7 是默认模型，3103/3105 都在线。链路通不通主要卡在 ephemeral 写入 → session-summary 生成这一步，之前那个空 summary 是因为上个 session 确实没有对话内容。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2364,"output":593,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23037,"cost":{"input":0.0007092,"output":0.0007116,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0026255999999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776179951716,"responseId":"062d8defb59820671f848a5675f8829a"}}
