{"type":"message","id":"0fac650e","parentId":"7503051f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:38:39.700Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User wants me to design a persona/profile recognition feature. This is a DESIGN type task - I need to provide background, plan comparison, and risk explanation.\n\nLet me think about what \"识别画像\" means in context. Given that this is an OpenClaw workspace, it could mean:\n1. User persona recognition (identifying who the user is based on their messages)\n2. Text/image analysis to extract persona characteristics\n3. Profile building from conversation context\n\nGiven the context - the user has been asking about the framework, SOUL.md, safety checks, etc. - this seems like they want a feature that can identify/classify user types or build user profiles.\n\nLet me design something useful but practical. I'll propose a concrete plan with actual implementation details.","thinkingSignature":"a363e71469d477e82b5efb8ebdb4fb84488451f9ea79460bc81ce4eb2f17ee09"},{"type":"text","text":"<thinking>\n### 1. 需求拆解\n用户需要一个\"识别画像\"功能。可能是：从对话内容中识别用户特征（偏好、技能水平、语气风格、意图模式），形成结构化画像，供后续个性化服务使用。\n\n### 2. 方案推演\n这是一个输入→分析→输出的 pipeline。我来设计一个轻量、可嵌入 OpenClaw 的画像系统。\n\n核心模块：\n1. **采集器**：从当前 session 提取消息特征（语言风格、提问类型、情感信号）\n2. **分析器**：调用已有的 3105 classifier 扩展 + 自定义画像规则\n3. **存储**：写入 memory/ 目录或 ephemeral\n\n画像维度建议：技能等级 / 沟通风格 / 关注领域 / 风险偏好 / 活跃时段\n\n### 3. 自我质疑\n这个 feature 具体要识别什么类型的画像？用户只说了\"识别画像\"四个字，没说输入是什么（纯文本？图片？对话历史？）。我需要先确认是做什么用的，再设计。\n</thinking>\n\n设计可以，但先问清楚——\"画像\"是指：\n\n1. **用户画像**：从对话历史里识别用户的技能水平、沟通风格、关注领域\n2. **文本画像**：给一段文本，提取作者的特征（语气、情绪、意图类型）\n3. **内容画像**：识别上传的图片/文件的特征标签\n4. **角色画像**：给一个角色描述，识别 MBTI/性格/行为模式\n\n哪个？还是混在一起说？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":465,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":23316,"totalTokens":23835,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.000558,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0087435,"total":0.0093177}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776181101537,"responseId":"062d926c5e0b54d2cd824c4f89deac7b"}}
