{"type":"message","id":"b276034b","parentId":"3cbac93d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:40:00.472Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they want to provide a piece of speech/text and have the system identify/profile it. So it's text-based profiling - extracting characteristics from the input text.\n\nLet me design a straightforward text profiling system that can analyze a piece of speech/text and identify various characteristics.","thinkingSignature":"28ace5a643328d628d8b2dc769619bd74e93e63b861b7dac5c3689a855412f8f"},{"type":"text","text":"那就做**文本画像**——输入一段话，输出作者/说话者的特征分析。\n\n---\n\n**画像维度（可配置）：**\n\n| 维度 | 分析内容 |\n|------|----------|\n| 语言风格 | 正式/随意/技术性/口语化 |\n| 情绪倾向 | 积极/中性/消极/愤怒/焦虑 |\n| 沟通意图 | 提问/陈述/指令/抱怨/闲聊 |\n| 专业程度 | 小白/入门/中级/专家 |\n| 行动倾向 | 高（明确要结果）/ 低（纯好奇） |\n| 隐含需求 | 可能需要什么帮助 |\n\n**输出格式：** 结构化 JSON + 一句话总结\n\n---\n\n**技术方案：**\n\n直接调现有的 3105 classifier（场景分类）扩展能力，额外加一层画像分析层。输入文本 → 3105 做意图分类 → 画像规则引擎输出画像标签。\n\n要我现在搭一个，还是先拿一段示例文本测一下效果？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":258,"cacheRead":23480,"cacheWrite":210,"totalTokens":24002,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0003096,"cacheRead":0.0014087999999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00007875,"total":0.0018133499999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776181190721,"responseId":"062d92c69048e3be80722ed0a214ea56"}}
