{"type":"message","id":"c263886f","parentId":"93f53f42","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:45:23.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if I can retrieve/search content from Xiaohongshu (小红书), a Chinese social media platform.\n\nI don't have a built-in tool for this. I can do web search via DuckDuckGo, and I can use web_fetch to extract content from URLs. If the user has a specific URL or search query, I could try fetching it.\n\nBut Xiaohongshu content is often behind login walls and its content is mostly in the app/web interface. I can try web_search or web_fetch, but it might be limited.","thinkingSignature":"b49fed2c777aa69b883051278132a138a4dfcb8064061590492b2f892c970151"},{"type":"text","text":"能用 web search + web fetch 抓取公开内容，但小红书有登录墙，限制比较多。\n\n有具体链接或关键词吗？我试试看。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":148,"cacheRead":23953,"cacheWrite":74,"totalTokens":24229,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00017759999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00143718,"cacheWrite":0.00002775,"total":0.00165873}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776181517648,"responseId":"062d940dbc182b41b4b95d813fdb2816"}}
