{"type":"message","id":"062ffa14","parentId":"088a6af5","timestamp":"2026-04-14T15:48:08.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to open up my思路 (thinking/mindset) and not rely solely on Brave. They're right - there are other ways to get web content. I can use web_fetch to directly fetch URLs, or I can think of other approaches. Actually, I could try fetching a xiaohongshu link directly with web_fetch if they have one. Or I could explore other search options.\n\nLet me be more open-ended and creative here. The user seems to want me to not be limited to just Brave search.","thinkingSignature":"d13f2b7734e8223fc6cbb578d1f7b8e570c3e6aca2d24657c00b34bef79e6a83"},{"type":"text","text":"不是，DuckDuckGo 也可以，还有 web_fetch 直接抓页面。\n\n你给我个链接，我用 web_fetch 直连试试看。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":139,"cacheRead":24357,"cacheWrite":97,"totalTokens":24647,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0001668,"cacheRead":0.00146142,"cacheWrite":0.000036375,"total":0.001680795}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776181683502,"responseId":"062d94b217f5bb13c57b0f75ddb0d732"}}
