{"type":"message","id":"cd13b5d2","parentId":"eb429d7d","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:06:22.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The xhs SDK is now working. It has all the methods needed:- `get_note_by_keyword` / `get_note_by_id` - search and read notes\n- `get_home_feed` - get feed\n- `get_user_info`, `get_user_notes` - user info\n- etc.\n\nNow the problem is that the SDK needs a cookie to work. Without a cookie, we can't actually search or read notes. The user needs to provide their Xiaohongshu cookie.\n\nLet me write a simple CLI wrapper script that makes it easy to use. But first, let me check if there's a way to use it without a cookie (maybe with just the sign function).","thinkingSignature":"534569551db74e580148e6dab4cfd7434c92e5c41041576b8478f2844e95fdfa"},{"type":"text","text":"SDK 跑通了！现在写个 CLI 封装，但需要你的 Cookie 才能真正调用 API。你有现成的小红书 Cookie 吗？或者用 Cookie-Editor 从浏览器导一个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":51143,"output":185,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71408,"cost":{"input":0.0153429,"output":0.000222,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0167697}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776182774043,"responseId":"062d98f5b6dbdbeb33fce7a25973e5d4"}}
