{"type":"message","id":"0f383bc3","parentId":"cf01357b","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:07:44.835Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to know how to get their Xiaohongshu cookie from a web browser. Let me explain the process.","thinkingSignature":"f9bad417bd450a5acf986a127b3b8e7c05e945dd05489f2615a09a23b971b8be"},{"type":"text","text":"Cookie-Editor 插件最简单：\n\n1. Chrome/Edge 装 [Cookie-Editor 插件](https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/cookie-editor/hlkenndednhfkekhgcdicdfddnkalmdm)\n2. 打开小红书网页版登录\n3. 点插件 → **Export** → 选 **Header String** 格式\n4. 把导出的整串 Cookie 发给我\n\n导出来大概长这样：\n```\na1=xxx; web_session=xxx; ...\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":138,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":47873,"totalTokens":68145,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0001656,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0.017952375,"total":0.019338974999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776182858034,"responseId":"062d994aa194bf221fb30c478387911e"}}
