{"type":"message","id":"57d45bd7","parentId":"a8befcca","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:12:58.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says the Cookie-Editor plugin doesn't work for them. There are other options to get the cookie. Let me think of alternatives:\n\n1. Browser DevTools - open Network tab, find a request to xiaohongshu.com, look at Request Headers for Cookie\n2. Use a script to extract from browser storage files directly\n3. Check if there's a simpler way\n\nFor Chrome on the user's local machine, they can:\n1. Open DevTools (F12) → Network tab → find a request to .xiaohongshu.com → Headers → Request Headers → copy Cookie value\n2. Or Application tab → Cookies\n\nThis requires them to do it manually on their browser and paste it to me.\n\n\nSince they can't export via the plugin, the most straightforward approach is to have them grab the cookie directly from DevTools and send it to me.","thinkingSignature":"b0e0c7e87d5dcffa223f4663a22d7c56d462e4d2db8925ac3748131b803891a7"},{"type":"text","text":"直接用浏览器开发者工具拿：\n\n1. 打开 Chrome/Edge，登录小红书网页版\n2. 按 **F12** 打开 DevTools\n3. 切到 **Network（网络）** 标签\n4. 随便点一个页面里的请求（比如刷新一下）\n5. 找到发往 `.xiaohongshu.com` 的请求，点进去\n6. 右边 **Headers** → **Request Headers** → 找 **Cookie:**\n7. 把整串 Cookie 值复制粘贴给我\n\n或者：\n- **Application** 标签 → **Cookies** → 选 `xiaohongshu.com` → 右边表格里有一堆 name=value，把它们拼成 `key1=val1; key2=val2; ...` 的格式发给我"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":68123,"totalTokens":68521,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0004128,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.025546125,"total":0.025975124999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776183163904,"responseId":"062d9a7b5b6b4571f3592ea0396a7bbe"}}
