{"type":"message","id":"c1d318e6","parentId":"8c578833","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:27:46.945Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Playwright and Chromium are available! Now I can try to use Playwright to log in to Xiaohongshu and extract cookies. But this requires user interaction (login with username/password or QR code scan). I can't do fully automated login unless the user provides credentials.\n\nLet me think... I could:\n1. Open the Xiaohongshu login page\n2. The user scans the QR code or enters credentials\n3. After login, I extract the cookies\n\nBut I'm a CLI tool, not a GUI. I can't display a QR code to the user in this chat interface. Unless I generate a QR code image and send it to the user.\n\nActually, Playwright can generate a QR code for login! Let me try:\n\n\nI'll launch a headless browser, navigate to the Xiaohongshu login page, and capture the QR code image so the user can scan it with their app.","thinkingSignature":"f77dcbe0aac602d6beecea2b04bda8f40e16025d77e697ca44408917945cc97d"},{"type":"text","text":"Playwright + Chromium 可用！可以自动打开浏览器拿 Cookie，但需要你扫码/登录。\n\n写个脚本——生成小红书登录二维码图片，你扫码后我自动提取 Cookie：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q27bodccsoq2_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/xhs_login.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"打开小红书登录页，生成二维码图片供扫码，然后导出 Cookie\"\"\"\n\nimport sys\nimport json\nimport base64\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\ndef main():\n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=False)  # 需要显示二维码\n        context = browser.new_context(viewport={\"width\": 400, \"height\": 700})\n        page = context.new_page()\n        \n        # 打开小红书登录页\n        page.goto(\"https://www.xiaohongshu.com\", timeout=30000)\n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # 点击登录按钮\n        try:\n            page.click('text=登录', timeout=5000)\n        except:\n            try:\n                page.click('text=登录/注册', timeout=5000)\n            except:\n                print(\"请手动点击登录按钮\")\n        \n        page.wait_for_timeout(2000)\n        \n        # 等待二维码出现\n        try:\n            qr_img = page.wait_for_selector('img[src*=\"qr\"]', timeout=10000)\n            qr_src = qr_img.get_attribute('src')\n            \n            if qr_src.startswith('data:image'):\n                # 保存二维码图片\n                img_data = qr_src.split(',')[1]\n                Path(\"/tmp/xhs_qr.png\").write_bytes(base64.b64decode(img_data))\n                print(\"二维码已保存到 /tmp/xhs_qr.png\")\n                print(\"请用小红书App扫码登录\")\n            else:\n                print(f\"二维码src: {qr_src}\")\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"等待二维码失败: {e}\")\n            # 截屏看看页面状态\n            page.screenshot(path=\"/tmp/xhs_login.png\")\n            print(\"截图已保存到 /tmp/xhs_login.png，请查看\")\n        \n        print(\"\\n扫码后在此窗口按回车继续...\")\n        input()\n        \n        # 提取 Cookie\n        cookies = context.cookies()\n        cookie_str = \"; \".join([f\"{c['name']}={c['value']}\" for c in cookies if 'xiaohongshu' in c.get('domain', '')])\n        \n        print(f\"\\nCookie 提取成功，共 {len(cookies)} 个小红书相关 Cookie\")\n        print(f\"Cookie 字符串前200字符:\\n{cookie_str[:200]}\")\n        \n        # 保存到文件\n        Path(\"/tmp/xhs_cookie.txt\").write_text(cookie_str)\n        print(f\"\\n已保存到 /tmp/xhs_cookie.txt\")\n        \n        # 也输出 JSON 格式（xhs SDK 用这个）\n        xhs_cookies = {c['name']: c['value'] for c in cookies if 'xiaohongshu' in c.get('domain', '')}\n        Path(\"/tmp/xhs_cookie.json\").write_text(json.dumps(xhs_cookies, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\n        print(f\"JSON 格式已保存到 /tmp/xhs_cookie.json\")\n        \n        browser.close()\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":51064,"output":916,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72060,"cost":{"input":0.0153192,"output":0.0010992,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0176232}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776184047939,"responseId":"062d9deffb66a5d7365995d2450742b1"}}
