{"type":"message","id":"4f524c14","parentId":"a3f84dc1","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:33:53.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `sign` function doesn't accept `web_session`. But `external_sign` in `_pre_headers` is called with `web_session`. Looking at line 142:\n\n```python\nself.external_sign(\n    url,\n    data,\n    a1=self.cookie_dict.get(\"a1\"),\n    web_session=self.cookie_dict.get(\"web_session\", \"\"),\n)\n```\n\nSo the SDK expects `external_sign` to be a custom sign function that accepts `web_session`. But the default `sign` from `xhs.help` doesn't accept it.\n\nThis means the SDK was designed to allow users to pass their own custom sign function that accepts `web_session`. \n\nIf no custom function is provided, I need to create a wrapper around the default `sign` that handles the `web_session` parameter gracefully by ignoring it.","thinkingSignature":"2f0f07c37bc16c437073dbe9464a1ecb74fd129e354dc90639f45256106dfa37"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mp72aogsrwwy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\ncontent = open('/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/xhs/core.py').read()\n\n# The external_sign default should wrap sign to accept web_session\nold = \"        from xhs.help import sign as _sign; self.external_sign = sign if sign is not None else _sign\\n\"\nnew = \"\"\"        from xhs.help import sign as _sign\n        if sign is not None:\n            self.external_sign = sign\n        else:\n            def _wrapper(uri, data=None, **kw):\n                return _sign(uri, data, a1=kw.get('a1',''))\n            self.external_sign = _wrapper\n\"\"\"\nif old in content:\n    content = content.replace(old, new)\n    open('/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/xhs/core.py', 'w').write(content)\n    print('fixed')\nelse:\n    print('pattern not found')\n    lines = content.split('\\n')\n    for i, line in enumerate(lines[98:110], start=99):\n        print(f\"{i}: {line}\")\nEOF\n","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58875,"output":433,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79388,"cost":{"input":0.017662499999999998,"output":0.0005195999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019386899999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776184423566,"responseId":"062d9f67ae51bec303a6b0eb5b7cb612"}}
