{"type":"message","id":"72b302b7","parentId":"8751b44a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:34:20.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great progress! Now the code is actually running and reaching the 小红书 API. The error is \"无登录信息，或登录信息为空\" which means the API requires login. The SDK needs a valid cookie to work.\n\nSo the situation is:\n1. The xhs SDK is installed and working (with our patches)\n2. It can make API calls but needs a valid cookie\n3. Without cookie, it returns \"no login info\"\n\nThis means the approach is fundamentally right - we DO need a cookie to search. So we're back to the original problem of needing the user's cookie.\n\nLet me summarize the situation clearly to the user: The SDK works but needs their 小红书 cookie. I can't browse the web without it.","thinkingSignature":"7a5ed9fd7955fb9e46c4348651bea01c63a8d0e30e98fef0db483eeedaa195c7"},{"type":"text","text":"SDK 本身完全跑通了——API 能请求，返回是 `无登录信息`，说明**必须有真实 Cookie 才能搜内容**。\n\n代码层面我已经把两个 bug 都修好了（Python 3.8 兼容问题 + sign 参数问题），但小红书 API 必须带有效 Cookie，这个绕不过去。\n\n---\n\n**结论：Cookie 是必需品，没它搜不了。**\n\n你现在有几个选项：\n\n1. **用 Playwright 自动扫码**（需要你操作一次）：\n   - 我生成登录二维码图片 → 你用小红书 App 扫码 → 我自动拿到 Cookie\n   - 只需要操作一次，之后一直能用\n\n2. **手动提供 Cookie**：\n   - Chrome 登录后，DevTools → Application → Cookies → 选 `xiaohongshu.com`\n   - 把 `web_session` 和 `a1` 这两个值发我（其他 SDK 会自动补）\n\n你想走哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":60186,"output":338,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80604,"cost":{"input":0.0180558,"output":0.0004056,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0196662}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776184447912,"responseId":"062d9f7f119472d91c06da93d5c543ae"}}
