{"type":"message","id":"183c1364","parentId":"a2fd3286","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:36:36.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is concerned that cookies expire. This is a valid concern - Xiaohongshu cookies do expire, typically within weeks or months. But:\n\n1. It's still the only way to access Xiaohongshu data via their API\n2. With a valid cookie, we can search and read content\n3. When it expires, they'd need to get a new one\n\nThe user seems to be looking for a more permanent solution. What are the alternatives?\n\n- **QR code login** - generates a login QR code, you scan with the Xiaohongshu app, and it gives you a token that might last longer than a cookie\n- **Phone login** - login with phone number + verification code\n\n\n- **Official API** - if they have developer access\n\nThe xhs SDK actually supports QR code login through the `get_qrcode()` and `check_qrcode()` methods, which is more stable than cookies since the QR code authenticates directly with the app. But the core issue remains - without some form of authentication, we can't access Xiaohongshu's data. The user might be suggesting that depending on cookies is unreliable, but I don't see another path forward here.","thinkingSignature":"714b85e65f9664657a686df623bdd8ba75e2264965e3c48bc45fa05994b716f1"},{"type":"text","text":"对，Cookie 会过期（通常几周到几个月）。\n\n但 QR 码登录不一样——它是用小红书 App 扫码，拿到的 token 有效期更长，而且可以随时续。\n\n我现在试试 QR 码方案：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w4yhiiymqqb8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages')\n\nfrom xhs import XhsClient\n\nc = XhsClient()\n\n# 获取二维码\ntry:\n    qr = c.get_qrcode()\n    print(\"QR code result:\")\n    import json\n    print(json.dumps(qr, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False))\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"错误: {type(e).__name__}: {e}\")\n    import traceback; traceback.print_exc()\nEOF\n","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":442,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":58054,"totalTokens":78630,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.0005304,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0.02177025,"total":0.02352165}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776184582395,"responseId":"062da006a4d4a4a3142fc688846c1afb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"352723e2","parentId":"183c1364","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:36:37.122Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_w4yhiiymqqb8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 10, in <module>\n  File \"/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/xhs/core.py\", line 636, in get_qrcode\n    return self.post(uri, data)\n  File \"/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/xhs/core.py\", line 194, in post\n    return self.request(\n  File \"/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/xhs/core.py\", line 181, in request\n    raise DataFetchError(data, response=response)\nxhs.exception.DataFetchError: {'code': -1, 'success': False}\n{'code': -1, 'success': False}\n错误: DataFetchError: {'code': -1, 'success': False}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":239,"aggregated":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<stdin>\", line 10, in <module>\n  File \"/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/xhs/core.py\", line 636, in get_qrcode\n    return self.post(uri, data)\n  File \"/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/xhs/core.py\", line 194, in post\n    return self.request(\n  File \"/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages/xhs/core.py\", line 181, in request\n    raise DataFetchError(data, response=response)\nxhs.exception.DataFetchError: {'code': -1, 'success': False}\n{'code': -1, 'success': False}\n错误: DataFetchError: {'code': -1, 'success': False}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776184597111}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2753260","parentId":"352723e2","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:36:48.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"QR code also fails without login. The SDK seems to require some level of authentication even for QR code generation.\n\nLet me think about this differently. Without any authentication, the xhs SDK can't do much. The user's point about cookies expiring is valid. \n\nWhat are the actual alternatives for getting long-term access to Xiaohongshu data?\n1. **QR code login** - should work without prior auth, but it's failing\n2. **Phone login** - `send_code()` and `check_code()` - might work without prior auth\n3. **Official Xiaohongshu API** - requires developer registration\n\nLet me try the phone login flow - send a verification code to the user's phone.\n\n\nThe real issue is that all these authentication methods need some form of identity to work with in the first place.","thinkingSignature":"2266e58ea0cf2c699c26fa696560af099b496aace134fc440be636fe9161dc7d"},{"type":"text","text":"QR 码也失败——看来 SDK 生成二维码也需要已登录状态。\n\n其实你说得对，Cookie 不是好方案。但换句话说——**不管哪种方式，最终都需要你本人授权一次**：\n\n- **Cookie**：每次过期要重新手动拿\n- **QR 码登录**：扫一次码，拿到的 token 可以维持更长时间，过期了再扫一次就行\n\n本质上没有\"不需要你操作\"的方案，因为小红书要求必须本人认证。\n\n你告诉我你想解决什么问题？是想让我能**搜小红书内容**，还是有别的目的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58741,"output":281,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79102,"cost":{"input":0.0176223,"output":0.0003372,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0191643}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776184597124,"responseId":"062da01465b5ba3fcf9f2598ddfdc913"}}
