{"type":"message","id":"55ca9506","parentId":"74f87ebe","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:38:18.646Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"But there's a problem - this script can't display the QR code in a headless environment. The QR code image is saved to /tmp/xhs_qr.png, but the user can't see it in the chat. I need to somehow display it to the user.Actually, the user is on a webchat interface. I can use the `image` tool to show the QR code if it's accessible, or I need to somehow render it in the chat. Let me check if the image_generate tool could help, or if I can encode the image as base64 and display it.Actually, I can read the image and show it using the image tool. Let me first generate the QR code.Actually wait - the QR code generation already failed with `{'code': -1, 'success': False}`. So the issue isn't displaying it, the issue is the QR code API itself is failing.\n\n\nLet me test the QR code endpoint directly to confirm what's actually happening.","thinkingSignature":"5fca45944fd4cf40d98481e8d4bfdbf92ab5aed057d59fb8697414757e454dc9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8l4x4deqsxmk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport sys\nsys.path.insert(0, '/home/ai/.local/lib/python3.8/site-packages')\nimport requests\nfrom xhs.help import sign\n\nuri = \"/api/sns/web/v1/login/qrcode/create\"\ndata = {}\na1 = \"187d2defea8dz1fgwydnci40kw265ikh9fsxn66qs50000726043\"\nsign_result = sign(uri, data, a1=a1)\nprint(\"sign:\", sign_result)\n\nhost = \"https://edith.xiaohongshu.com\"\nheaders = {\n    \"user-agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/111.0.0.0 Safari/537.36\",\n    \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\",\n    \"x-s\": sign_result[\"x-s\"],\n    \"x-t\": sign_result[\"x-t\"],\n    \"x-s-common\": sign_result[\"x-s-common\"],\n}\nimport json\njson_str = json.dumps(data, separators=(\",\", \":\"), ensure_ascii=False)\nresp = requests.post(f\"{host}{uri}\", data=json_str.encode(), headers=headers, timeout=10)\nprint(\"status:\", resp.status_code)\nprint(\"response:\", resp.text[:500])\nEOF\n","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61145,"output":520,"cacheRead":20080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81745,"cost":{"input":0.0183435,"output":0.000624,"cacheRead":0.0012047999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.020172299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776184686035,"responseId":"062da06d8dded7520132dfaeefd1fb80"}}
