{"type":"message","id":"96c99656","parentId":"44372751","timestamp":"2026-04-14T16:45:18.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"User is frustrated and calling me out. They said \"我看你在放屁\" which means \"I think you're talking nonsense\" or \"bullshit.\"\n\nThey're right to be frustrated. I've been going in circles for a while - talking about cookies, QR codes, proxies, Playwright, etc. - and haven't actually delivered anything working.\n\nLet me think about what actually matters:\n1. The user wanted to search 小红书 content\n2. I've been jumping through hoops trying to get authentication working\n3. I haven't actually delivered any useful functionality yet\n\nThe honest truth: without a valid session (Cookie/token), I can't search 小红书. The options are:\n1. They give me a working Cookie (but it expires and IP issues)\n\n\n2. I use Playwright on their machine (but that requires running code on their Windows machine)\n3. There's a proxy so IPs match\n\nBut really - what are they actually trying to accomplish? They asked me to \"发散一下思维\" about getting 小红书 content. I found Agent-Reach, installed xhs, fixed bugs. But none of it works without authentication.\n\nThe fundamental problem is this is a sandboxed environment with different IP from the user, and 小红书 has authentication + IP-based blocking. I should be honest that I'm hitting a wall here and ask what specifically they were hoping to accomplish.","thinkingSignature":"05bac49ab6f76730aece3f092ad339a0f9b93a1aa65132e9c6ad5d3c064a4c51"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，绕了一大圈什么都没跑通。\n\n核心问题就一个：这个沙盒和你的网络是隔离的，小红书认 IP，不管拿什么 Cookie 都没用。\n\n诚实说——**这个环境直接搜小红书走不通**，不管换什么工具。\n\n如果你真想让我能搜，唯一办法是你本地装个 agent-reach 让它连上来，但那是你本地机器的事，不是我这边能搞定的。\n\n你想搜小红书内容是为了什么？有没有别的我能直接帮上的忙？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":381,"cacheRead":84695,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85076,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0004572,"cacheRead":0.0050817,"cacheWrite":0,"